cs.EM, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.EM (Embedded Systems) is the most likely category as the paper deals with formalizing real-time systems, which are a subset of embedded systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also likely as the paper discusses a tool for translating a graphical specification into a formalism equipped with a formal semantics. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper mentions the use of parametric timed automata, which are a type of formalism used in programming languages. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper deals with formal analysis of real-time systems, which involves logical reasoning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with real-time systems, which are a type of control system.
